import Head from 'next/head'
import Layouts from '../Components/Layouts/Layouts'

import HomeSection from '../Components/Home/Home'
const Index = () => {
    
    
    return (
        
        <>
        <Head>
          <title>React</title>

        <BrowserRouter>

        <Layouts>

}

export default Index
